[
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=2"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hello, and welcome to ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Discover rolling clips with ReplayKit.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=10"
  },
  {
    "text": "My name is Ernest, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "and I'm a software engineer on the ReplayKit team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=14"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today, I'm really excited to show you a new way ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=17"
  },
  {
    "text": "to capture your application highlights. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=19"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let me start by giving you an overview of ReplayKit.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=22"
  },
  {
    "text": "ReplayKit is a framework that enables you to record ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=26"
  },
  {
    "text": "your application's screen and audio. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=29"
  },
  {
    "text": "When people want to make an instructional video, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=32"
  },
  {
    "text": "or simply just wanna show off their gameplay, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=34"
  },
  {
    "text": "in-app screen recording creates a video ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=37"
  },
  {
    "text": "that they can save and share with their friends. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "And what if you wanted more control over ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=41"
  },
  {
    "text": "the video content people create? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=43"
  },
  {
    "text": "You may want to add additional filters, or overlays. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=45"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can do this with in-app screen capture. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=48"
  },
  {
    "text": "In-app screen capture will give the audio and video samples ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=51"
  },
  {
    "text": "directly to your application process, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=55"
  },
  {
    "text": "so you'll have complete control ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=57"
  },
  {
    "text": "over the content that is being created. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=58"
  },
  {
    "text": "And we all know the next best thing to playing a game ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "is watching gameplay live. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=64"
  },
  {
    "text": "In-app broadcast makes it easy for people ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=67"
  },
  {
    "text": "to stream your application to third-party broadcast services, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=68"
  },
  {
    "text": "to be viewed all around the world. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=72"
  },
  {
    "text": "While our current recording features cover a wide variety ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=76"
  },
  {
    "text": "of use cases, there is one that we currently don't. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=79"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, imagine your players just fought all the enemies ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=83"
  },
  {
    "text": "and unlocked the key to a level in your game, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=85"
  },
  {
    "text": "and now they wanna share that moment with their friends. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=87"
  },
  {
    "text": "But because it's their first time playing this level, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=90"
  },
  {
    "text": "they didn't know something exciting was gonna happen, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=93"
  },
  {
    "text": "and they weren't able to capture that moment. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=95"
  },
  {
    "text": "Currently, players will need to record ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=98"
  },
  {
    "text": "their entire gameplay in order to save ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "all their memorable highlights. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=102"
  },
  {
    "text": "This results in a large recording that will ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=104"
  },
  {
    "text": "not only take up a lot of space, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=106"
  },
  {
    "text": "but will require time to trim into shorter clips. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=108"
  },
  {
    "text": "Wouldn't it be awesome if you could record ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=112"
  },
  {
    "text": "all the highlights right when they happen? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=114"
  },
  {
    "text": "Or even better, what if ReplayKit does this for you, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=117"
  },
  {
    "text": "and gives you the video clip of each moment? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=120"
  },
  {
    "text": "This year, I'm excited to show you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=124"
  },
  {
    "text": "a new feature we've been working on, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=126"
  },
  {
    "text": "clips recording. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=129"
  },
  {
    "text": "Clips recording will keep a rolling buffer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=132"
  },
  {
    "text": "of audio and video samples. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=134"
  },
  {
    "text": "When clip export is called, the samples up to 15 seconds prior ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=136"
  },
  {
    "text": "can be exported into a short video clip. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=141"
  },
  {
    "text": "So now, instead of needing to know when to Start Recording, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=144"
  },
  {
    "text": "you just need to know when you want to export.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are several ways to export a video clip. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=151"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can add UI buttons or a game controller support ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=153"
  },
  {
    "text": "to your application, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=156"
  },
  {
    "text": "so people can have manual control ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=158"
  },
  {
    "text": "on when to capture clips. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=159"
  },
  {
    "text": "With the tap of a button, they can ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=162"
  },
  {
    "text": "get the clip exactly when they want it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=164"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can also add triggers in your application ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=167"
  },
  {
    "text": "that will automatically capture clips. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=169"
  },
  {
    "text": "With this, you will always capture ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=171"
  },
  {
    "text": "those exciting moments when they get a perfect combo, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=173"
  },
  {
    "text": "defeat the final boss, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=176"
  },
  {
    "text": "or beat their best speed run. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=178"
  },
  {
    "text": "And with all of these clips, you can create ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=180"
  },
  {
    "text": "personalized user experiences. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "You could add a custom overlay that opens ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=186"
  },
  {
    "text": "to a collection of recordings, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "or you could present a highlight reel ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=189"
  },
  {
    "text": "with all the clips captured at the end of a level ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=191"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your players to see and share.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=193"
  },
  {
    "text": "Clips recording will be available for iOS and macOS, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=197"
  },
  {
    "text": "and is a powerful feature that will sit alongside ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=201"
  },
  {
    "text": "our existing recording, capture, and broadcast APIs. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=203"
  },
  {
    "text": "Similar to our other features, clips recording will provide ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=209"
  },
  {
    "text": "the same HD quality, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=212"
  },
  {
    "text": "low-performance impact, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "and built-in privacy safeguards. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=216"
  },
  {
    "text": "How does clips recording work under the hood? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=218"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take a look. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=221"
  },
  {
    "text": "Clips recording includes three APIs: start, stop, and export. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=223"
  },
  {
    "text": "To start clip buffering, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=229"
  },
  {
    "text": "your application should call into RPScreenRecorder ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=231"
  },
  {
    "text": "to get the sharedRecorder singleton instance. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=233"
  },
  {
    "text": "With the shared instance, you can ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=236"
  },
  {
    "text": "call the startClipBuffering API. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=238"
  },
  {
    "text": "At which point, ReplayKit will store screen ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "and audio samples from your application in a rolling buffer. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=243"
  },
  {
    "text": "Every time ReplayKit receives new samples, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=247"
  },
  {
    "text": "any samples older than 15 seconds will be discarded. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=250"
  },
  {
    "text": "After the rolling buffer starts, ReplayKit ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=254"
  },
  {
    "text": "waits for your application to tell it to export. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=257"
  },
  {
    "text": "When the application calls the export clip API, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=260"
  },
  {
    "text": "ReplayKit takes care of the rest and returns you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=264"
  },
  {
    "text": "the video clip of that moment. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=266"
  },
  {
    "text": "When you no longer need the rolling buffer, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=269"
  },
  {
    "text": "or when you want to use another ReplayKit feature, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=272"
  },
  {
    "text": "such as in-app broadcast, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=274"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can call the stop API, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=276"
  },
  {
    "text": "and ReplayKit will tear down the session.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=278"
  },
  {
    "text": "With this information in mind, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "let me show you a sample project ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=284"
  },
  {
    "text": "that implements the new clips APIs.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=285"
  },
  {
    "text": "You may already be familiar with this sample project ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=289"
  },
  {
    "text": "from our session last year. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=291"
  },
  {
    "text": "The updated sample project now includes code for clips. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=293"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take a look at this code. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=297"
  },
  {
    "text": "Just like the other recording sessions, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=300"
  },
  {
    "text": "here's the IBAction associated with the \"start clips\" button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=302"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the main storyboard. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=305"
  },
  {
    "text": "This button is used to start clip buffering ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=307"
  },
  {
    "text": "if you aren't already active, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=309"
  },
  {
    "text": "and stop clip buffering if you are active. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=311"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let's go ahead and take a look at ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=314"
  },
  {
    "text": "what happens when you start clip buffering. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=316"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here is the code to start clip buffering. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=320"
  },
  {
    "text": "You're going to get the shared recorder instance ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=322"
  },
  {
    "text": "from RPScreenRecorder and call startClipBuffering ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=324"
  },
  {
    "text": "with your completion handler. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=328"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here, within the completion handler, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=330"
  },
  {
    "text": "you will need to handle any error that occurred ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=332"
  },
  {
    "text": "while attempting to start, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=334"
  },
  {
    "text": "including updating the UI. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=335"
  },
  {
    "text": "If there's no error, then you should also update the UI ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=338"
  },
  {
    "text": "to show that the recording is currently active.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=341"
  },
  {
    "text": "Similar to start, there's a stop clip ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=345"
  },
  {
    "text": "buffering method in the sample project. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=347"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is where you're going to get the shared instance, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=350"
  },
  {
    "text": "but this time, you'll call the stopClipBuffering API. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=352"
  },
  {
    "text": "In the completion handler, you will need to handle ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=356"
  },
  {
    "text": "any error that occurred while attempting to stop, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=358"
  },
  {
    "text": "and should update the UI to show that you're no longer recording.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=361"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now that I went through the code for start ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=366"
  },
  {
    "text": "and stop clip buffering, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=368"
  },
  {
    "text": "let's look at the code needed to export a clip. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=370"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is the code for the IBAction ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=373"
  },
  {
    "text": "associated with the \"export clip\" button. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=374"
  },
  {
    "text": "The action is triggered when a person decides ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=378"
  },
  {
    "text": "they want to generate a clip. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=380"
  },
  {
    "text": "Just a reminder that you're not limited ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=382"
  },
  {
    "text": "by this approach and may export clips automatically ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=384"
  },
  {
    "text": "based on your own application triggers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=388"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here, if you're actively recording and the button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=391"
  },
  {
    "text": "is enabled from the previous startClipBuffering method, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=394"
  },
  {
    "text": "the exportClip function will be called. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=398"
  },
  {
    "text": "To call the exportClip API, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=401"
  },
  {
    "text": "you will need to specify a URL and a clip duration.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=403"
  },
  {
    "text": "Similar to the start and stop APIs, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=410"
  },
  {
    "text": "you will then handle any errors in the completionHandler. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=412"
  },
  {
    "text": "If there's no error, then you should have ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=416"
  },
  {
    "text": "the clip at the specified URL. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=418"
  },
  {
    "text": "With access to the clips, you can then build and organize ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=421"
  },
  {
    "text": "your own user experiences. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=424"
  },
  {
    "text": "In my sample code here, the clip is simply saved to Photos.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=427"
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's it! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=433"
  },
  {
    "text": "With these three APIs, you can now add clips recording ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=435"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your application. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=438"
  },
  {
    "text": "You will have direct access to the clips in the specified URL, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=439"
  },
  {
    "text": "so you can build your own in-app experiences. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=443"
  },
  {
    "text": "As previously mentioned, another way to get clips ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=446"
  },
  {
    "text": "is by adding game controller support. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=449"
  },
  {
    "text": "The game controller framework will now have ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=452"
  },
  {
    "text": "built-in clips recording. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=455"
  },
  {
    "text": "Keep in mind, clips exported from the game controller ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=457"
  },
  {
    "text": "will save directly to Photos or the Desktop. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=460"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, to make your own in-app experiences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=463"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the generated clips, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=465"
  },
  {
    "text": "you will need to implement the ReplayKit clips API. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=467"
  },
  {
    "text": "When integrating both ReplayKit ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=471"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the game controller framework, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=473"
  },
  {
    "text": "it is good idea to make sure ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=475"
  },
  {
    "text": "you're using key value observing for both available ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=476"
  },
  {
    "text": "and recording properties on RPScreenRecorder. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=480"
  },
  {
    "text": "Also be sure to follow the protocol ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=484"
  },
  {
    "text": "RPScreenRecorderDelegate so that you can update ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=486"
  },
  {
    "text": "your application's state as needed. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=489"
  },
  {
    "text": "And it's that simple to integrate clips recording ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=493"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your applications. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=495"
  },
  {
    "text": "With clips recording, your application will be ready ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=497"
  },
  {
    "text": "to capture all of the exciting moments when they happen. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=500"
  },
  {
    "text": "I look forward to seeing all of the clips ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=503"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the new user experiences you will create. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=506"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you so much for watching our session. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=509"
  },
  {
    "text": "I hope you have a wonderful WWDC. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=511"
  },
  {
    "text": "[percussive music]",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10101/?time=514"
  }
]